# Wallet Setup Guide

## Setting up Coinbase Wallet for Base

### Step 1 — Install Coinbase Wallet
Download from coinbase.com/wallet
Available on iOS, Android, and browser extension.

### Step 2 — Create a wallet
Open the app and select Create new wallet.
Write down your 12-word recovery phrase and store
it somewhere safe offline. Never share it.

### Step 3 — Add Base network
Base is added automatically in Coinbase Wallet.
For MetaMask add manually:
- Network name: Base
- RPC URL: https://mainnet.base.org
- Chain ID: 8453
- Symbol: ETH
- Explorer: https://basescan.org

### Step 4 — Get Base ETH
- Buy ETH on Coinbase and bridge to Base
- Or bridge from Ethereum at bridge.base.org

### Step 5 — Get testnet ETH
For Base Sepolia testing:
- Visit faucet.quicknode.com
- Select Base Sepolia
- Paste your wallet address
- Receive free test ETH